      "title": "India needs many big-ticket exports like BrahMos deal to hit $5 billion export target by 2025, counter China\r",
      "desc": "India needs several big-ticket deals like the one recently closed with the Philippines for BrahMos missile worth $375 million, to reach $5 billion export target by 2025 and counter China.\r",
