      "title": "Ukraine crisis: India calls for ‘peaceful resolution’\r",
      "desc": "The Indian government’s position was articulated by the Ministry of External Affairs’ official spokesperson Arindam Bagchi at the weekly briefing Friday.\r",
      "image": "https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_nbcnews-fp-1200-630,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2022_04/3530240/220118-russian-convoy-soldiers-ew-131p.jpg",
